The '''Rodian Council of Justice''' was an organization on [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. Its role was to verify kills made by [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]], normally requiring pieces of the victim as evidence. This led to many Rodian hunters favoring [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonators]] and [[Grenade/Legends|grenades]] as they always left plenty of pieces and witnesses to the kill.

